te Web',6,NULL,'d20 + RL / 2 + Dex mod + range mod + PAM + AB vs. Ref','6 AP (once/r)','C','5 SP','10 sq\\n (2 sq increment)','Instantaneous','1 sq','You throw a web at the chosen square.','S - Affected target is entangled.\\nCS - The target is entangled and unable to leave its square.\\nF - The target is not entangled, but the area is still considered difficult terrain.',NULL,NULL,NULL),(239,'Ground Manipulation',11,'[Su]',NULL,'9 AP','C','2 SP','0','Instantaneous','1 sq radius','You turn stone and earth in adjacent squares to mud (triple movement cost).',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(240,'Siren Song',11,'[Su, Mind]','d20 + Body & Mind skill mod + Cha mod + PAM + AB vs. Will','6 AP (once/r)','C, V','10 PP','0','Concentration + 1 r','60 sq spread','You captivate living creatures within range.','S - Victims walk toward the singer and then stop within 1 sq, offering no resistance whatsoever.\\nF - Target is unaffected.',NULL,NULL,NULL),(241,'Forge Painting',10,'[Untrained, Secret]','d20 + Crafting (Painting) skill + Int mod vs. opposing Perception','Var','Hands, tools','Materials','Tch','Instantaneous','1 painting','You try to copy a painting or the style of a certain artist.','S – You make a forgery that fools the viewer.\\nF – The viewer recognizes your painting as a forgery.',NULL,NULL,NULL);
