INSERT INTO `implementtypes` VALUES (1,'Concentration','C         ','You need a certain amount of focus and concentration to perform the action. If you perform the action while you are already maintaining concentration on another action, you lose the earlier action.'),(2,'Verbal','V         ','You need to be able to speak in a firm voice. Typically, you have to use a language, but the targets (if any) do not need to understand the language. If you are deafened, you suffer a -4 circumstance penalty on the action check. Creatures without true languages (such as animals) cannot perform actions that require a verbal component.'),(3,'Somatic','S         ','You need to be able to gesticulate clearly with one or more hands; at least one hand must be empty and free to move. However, some special actions allow special implements to be used in place of hands; for example, wands can be used for arcane spellcasting and holy symbols for divine spellcasting.'),(4,'Material','M         ','You need to use one or more consumables. The action’s activation time assumes that the material is easy to reach (in a belt pouch, for instance, and not in a backpack). Otherwise, add the time required to find and retrieve the material.'),(5,'Focus','F         ','You need a catalyst that is not consumed by the action. The action’s activation time assumes that the focus is easy to reach (in a belt pouch or around the neck, for instance, and not in a backpack).'),(6,'Vision','vis       ','You need eyes or an equivalent sense of vision. Vision-related modifiers may apply to the action.'),(7,'Hearing','aud       ','You need ears or an equivalent sense of hearing. Hearing-related modifiers may apply to the action.'),(8,'Touch','tch       ','You need a sense of touch.'),(9,'Smell','sml','You need a sense of smell.');
